data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom 2 bath home in DeCordova Bend Estates with a Pool!  This is the perfect move-in ready home with an oasis in your backyard. Kitchen is perfect for entertaining with an open concept floor plan. Beautiful granite countertops throughout, fireplace, high ceilings, and upgraded wood tile throughout main portion of house. Backyard is the perfect spot to relax after a long day. Enjoy the saltwater pool, plenty of room for your pets to run around and a privacy fence.
